1. Rules

The idea of this game is to turn all your enemies pieces into your own, this is
done by making one of your atom's to explode converting any atoms horizontaly
or verticaly ajacent to your own into your colour.

Deadend 1 explode.
Corners 2 explode.
Edges   3 explode.
Other   4 explode.

2. Controls

The controls are as follows:

Very simple just click on the square you want to power up.

The intelligence of the computer players can be altered by the tooltypes

    A1=
    A2=
    A3=

They can be set to 0 of greater.

3. Additional Information

This program will only work on WB 3.0 AGA and above.

This program was written on an Amiga A1200 68882 6MB.

The sound can be turned off and on by altering the tool type.

GUI designed with gadtoolsbox.

DICE C used for coding;

